Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm going to get changed...}Tôi đi thay đồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{so please wait there for a bit.}nên anh hãy chờ ở đó nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, hold up a second.}{\i0}Này này, khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're seriously going to get changed now?}{\i0}Định thay đồ ở đây hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{With me right here?}{\i0}Ngay trước mắt mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ực.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ta-da!}Xem nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When I get changed...}Khi thay đồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I just put this corset on\Nover my clothes, that's all!}Tôi sẽ chỉ đeo cái nịt này vào và thế là xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oink.}{\i0}Éc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Um, I'm very sorry\Nfor not living up to your expectations.}Tôi xin lỗi vì khiến anh kì vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I thought you'd like it,\Nand I got the urge to play a little trick on you.}Cứ tưởng anh thích nên định trêu một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, no!}{\i0}À không!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not like I was expecting anything!}{\i0}Tôi có kì vọng gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, right.}{\i0}A phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She can read my mind, can't she?}{\i0}Có thể đọc tâm trí...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All I meant was that maybe I could see you\Nin a different outfit, okay?}{\i0}Cái đó tôi chỉ muốn thấy Jess mặc bộ đồ khác thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I wasn't hoping to see you change\Nright in front of me! No way!}{\i0}Chứ không phải muốn cô thay đồ trước mặt đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, I'll be sure to let you see me\Nwearing something else sometime.}Vậy thì lần tới tôi sẽ chuẩn bị một bộ khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah! That would be great.}{\i0}Ừ! Nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Still, not only can this girl\Nread people's minds...}{\i0}Cơ mà không chỉ đọc tâm trí...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{but she also perceived my buried desire\Nto be tormented by a beautiful young girl!}{\i0}cô ấy cũng biết được khao khát cháy bỏng muốn\N được một mỹ nữ xinh đẹp chà đạp của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{If that's the case, how terrifying.}{\i0}Nếu là thế thì thật kinh khủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Mister Pig...}Anh Heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's the town of Kiltyrie!}Kia là thị trấn Kiltyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh!}{\i0}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's go!}Đi thôi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah!}{\i0}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Apologies, gentlemen...}{\i0}Xin lỗi nhé các chàng trai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but I'm going one level higher.}{\i0}anh đây tiến hoá lên bậc cao trước nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We're about to go on a shopping date.}{\i0}Bọn này đang đi mua sắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can at least watch\Nand learn from my exploits.}{\i0}Các cậu ở đó xem mà học hỏi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's so lively! What a nice little town!}{\i0}Thị trấn náo nhiệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I was worried you'd stick out,\Nroaming the streets with a pig in tow...}{\i0}Cứ tưởng dẫn một con\N heo vào thành phố sẽ nổi bật lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but those fears were groundless.}{\i0}nhưng có vẻ không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's an isekai,\Nbut I'm only seeing normal animals.}{\i0}Đây là dị giới, cơ mà toàn thấy động vật bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not a bizarre-looking monster in sight.}{\i0}Không thấy con quái kì lạ nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is there some kind of event going on?}{\i0}Có sự kiện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh!}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They're holding a festival tonight.}Tối nay họ tổ chức lễ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Mister Pig, you're fond of festivals, I see.}Anh Heo thích lễ hội nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I like that out-of-the-ordinary vibe.}{\i0}Vì không khí khác hẳn ngày thường mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Festivals are like that,\Nand so's traveling.}{\i0}Lễ hội mang đến sự náo nhiệt và du hành.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{"Travel," did you say?}Du hành à...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Haven't you ever gone on a trip, Jess?}{\i0}Cô từng đi du hành chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, not once.}Chưa lần nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, going to the royal capital\Nwill be your first-ever trip?}{\i0}Tức là đến thủ đô là chuyến đi xa đầu tiên?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's something to look forward to!}{\i0}Mong chờ ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Something... to look forward to, right?}Đúng là... đáng mong chờ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Oink.}{\i0}Éc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, what kind of shop is that?}{\i0}Jess, kia là cửa hàng gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's a rista shop.}A, là cửa hàng rista.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's where I always buy them.}Là nơi tôi hay mua chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's some hard-core security there.}{\i0}Bảo vệ kĩ càng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because rista are very expensive.}Vì rista rất quý giá mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess...}{\i0}Nè Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What did you come here for, exactly?}{\i0}Sao chúng ta lại đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There are all kinds of reasons, you see...}Có nhiều lý do lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please, stay close to me, will you?}{\i0}Hãy đi sát lại gần tôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What was that?}{\i0}Vừa rồi là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yethmas aren't just able\Nto read people's minds.}{\i0}Yethmas không chỉ đọc tâm trí người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We can also communicate\Nour own inner thoughts.}{\i0}Mà còn có thể truyền đạt suy nghĩ của bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I believe it would be better\Nnot to speak out loud that much here.}{\i0}Tôi nghĩ từ đây không nên nói chuyện nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see. Huh?}{\i0}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hold up a second!}{\i0}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In no way is this any place\Nfor a girl to come alone!}{\i0}Nơi này sao để con gái vào được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{As long as I have this, I'll be fine.}{\i0}Miễn là còn thứ này thì không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What is that?}{\i0}Đó là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If they see this House Kiltyrin crest...}{\i0}Nếu họ thấy gia huy nhà Kiltyrin..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{no one will even think of attacking me.}{\i0}thì sẽ không ai dám tấn công.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Doesn't that mean that without it,\Nyou'd have to worry about being attacked?}{\i0}Tức là không có nó thì bị tấn công hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If it comes to that, I mean.}{\i0}Chỉ là nếu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And anyway, I have you, Mister Pig!}{\i0}Và tôi còn có anh bên cạnh mà, anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not a lot I can do in a pig's body, though.}{\i0}Cô nghĩ một con heo thì làm được gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Fine! I'll be your guard!}{\i0}Mà thôi, tôi sẽ bảo vệ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thank you very much!}{\i0}Cảm ơn anh nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Little Miss Yethma!}Tiểu thư Yethma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you've come here all by yourself,\Nyou must be doing some covert shopping.}Đến đây một mình tức là đang mua sắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is this what you want?}Đây là thứ cô muốn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Black rista, three for 400 golts.}rista đen, 400 golt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's a bargain!}Giảm giá đặc biệt nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{At that price?}Rẻ vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They're all you need\Nto make wishes come true!}Chỉ với cái giá đó là biến\N ước mơ thành sự thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can't get them for this price\Nanywhere else.}Không kiếm được mối ngon hơn đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I'm sorry...}Nhưng tôi xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't have 400.}Tôi không có 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{How much will just one cost?}Một cái giá bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{One, huh?}Một à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can give you one for 150 golts.}Một cái 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can pay you 150 golts.}Nếu là 150...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess...}{\i0}Này Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You told me that Yethmas used\Nblack rista for prayer.}{\i0}Cô nói Yethma dùng rista đen để cầu nguyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How many would you need for one session?}{\i0}Một lần cần bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{One would be enough.}{\i0}Thường thì một là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is there ever any leftover magic power\Nafter a wish has been granted?}{\i0}Sau khi hoàn thành điều ước\N thì còn sót lại ma lực không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes, usually there's some left over.}{\i0}Vâng, thường thì còn lại một ít.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, young miss, what's the problem?}Này, sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, pretend you're chasing after me\Nand follow my lead!}{\i0}Jess, giả bộ đuổi theo tôi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh...}A...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry!}Tôi xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey! Miss!}Này! Tiểu thư!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What just happened, exactly?}Chuyện gì vừa xảy ra vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Jess, you'd better not buy\Nany rista from that man.}{\i0}Jess, cô không nên mua rista từ hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But why not?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Those rista are all probably used,\Nwith just some dregs left over.}{\i0}Chúng là hàng đã xài rồi,\N chỉ còn một ít ma lực sót lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{One black rista\Nis all you need to grant a wish.}{\i0}Một rista đen sẽ hoàn thành điều ước.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't that what you told me?}{\i0}Cô nói thế phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But that guy said,\N"Three for 400 golts.}{\i0}Nhưng tên đó nói 3 cái 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They're all you need\Nto make wishes come true."}{\i0}Chỉ cần như thế là ước mơ thành hiện thực...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's true, with three,\Nyou could make lots of wishes come true.}Đúng là với 3 cái thì có thể biến\N giấc mơ thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't give it such a positive spin!}{\i0}Đừng cả tin như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What he meant was, with three of them,\Nyou might make one wish come true.}{\i0}Ý hắn là với 3 cái thì có thể \Nbiến 1 điều ước thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Think about it.}{\i0}Nghĩ kĩ xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{A Yethma who has to buy\Nblack rista in a place like that...}{\i0}Một Yethma mua rista đen ở nơi mờ ám...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{normally wouldn't shop in one of those places\Non the main road, would she?}{\i0}chẳng phải nên mua nó ở cửa hàng khi nãy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In fact, not many houses own black rista\Nin the first place.}Với cả không nhiều nơi có bán rista đen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If the customer was someone\Nwho'd never used a real black rista,}{\i0}Nếu khách hàng là người chưa từng dùng đến,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{you wouldn't get caught\Nselling her shoddy goods.}{\i0}thì sẽ không thể biết nếu hàng kém chất lượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can read my mind, can't you?}{\i0}Cô có thể đọc tâm trí phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The instant he saw your corset,\Nhe started acting totally sketchy.}{\i0}Khi thấy nịt bụng đó, hắn bắt đầu trở nên kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It did seem like he was uncomfortable\Nabout something...}Có vẻ hắn cảm thấy không thoải mái gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{but I couldn't hear his thoughts\Nin more detail.}nhưng tôi không thể đọc được chi tiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Still, that guy's doing business\Nwith Yethmas who can read his mind.}{\i0}Tên đó buôn bán với một Yethma đọc tâm trí...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's probably being careful\Nnot to transmit his evil intentions.}{\i0}Hẳn hắn đã giấu đi ý đồ xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess he realized\Nyou were a Yethma from House Kiltyrin.}{\i0}Tôi đoán hắn đã nhận ra cô là Yethma từ nhà Kiltyrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That you might be a Yethma\Nwho's handled real black rista before.}{\i0}Rằng có thể cô từng sử dụng qua rista đen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So if he sold you inferior goods...}{\i0}Nếu bán cô sản phẩm lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{word of his shameful shenanigans\Ncould reach your masters, House Kiltyrin.}{\i0}việc đó sẽ đến tai nhà Kiltyrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That must've made him wary.}{\i0}Nên đã khiến hắn cảnh giác.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, so that's what was going on.}A, hoá ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought they were quite cheap.}Tôi tưởng chúng rẻ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How much is one normally?}{\i0}Thế bình thường 1 cái bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{At the shop I usually buy them from...}Ở cửa hàng hay mua...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{one costs 600 golts.}thì một cái 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, come on!\NThat should've tipped you off right there!}{\i0}Này này! Đáng ra phải nghi ngờ rồi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Since he'd been kind enough to call out to me,\NI felt bad about suspecting him.}Dù gì hắn đã gọi tôi nên lờ đi có hơi thất lễ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, that was my monologue just now.}{\i0}Không không, vừa rồi tôi độc thoại.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ignore it.}{\i0}Đừng nghĩ đến nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're right! Sorry about that.}A, phải nhỉ! Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Still, I already knew you were too nice...}{\i0}Cơ mà biết là cô tốt bụng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but this is next-level.}{\i0}nhưng cái này tốt quá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig...}Anh heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If it hadn't been for you, Mister Pig,}Nếu không có anh ở đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I would've been swindled\Nout of my precious money.}tôi đã phí phạm tiền bạc rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, don't mention it!}{\i0}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But be on the alert from now on!}{\i0}Nhưng lần tới phải cảnh giác đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Anyone who offers you a huge discount\Nusually only has his own profit in mind.}{\i0}Bất kì kẻ nào giảm giá\N quá nhiều thì hãy suy nghĩ lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, by the way...}{\i0}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{why were you secretly trying\Nto buy a black rista anyway, Jess?}{\i0}sao cô lại bí mật đi mua rista đen thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Can't I say it's a secret\Nand leave it at that?}Cứ xem đó như bí mật và bỏ qua nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{When I was in the pigpen, I couldn't\Nunderstand what you were saying.}{\i0}Khi trong chuồng heo, tôi đã không hiểu cô nói gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{And I hadn't yet adapted\Nto being in a pig's body.}{\i0}Và vẫn chưa quen với cơ thể một con heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But ever since I woke up in your room,\NI could understand what you were saying,}{\i0}Nhưng sau khi tỉnh lại trong\N phòng cô, tôi lại hiểu tiếng nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{my eyesight went back to normal,\Nand I could walk on all fours.}{\i0}Tầm nhìn quay lại và có thể đi bằng 4 chân.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You told me you'd done\Neverything you could...}{\i0}Jess nói đã làm mọi thứ với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but what was it that you did for me?}{\i0}nhưng rốt cuộc cô đã làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If I've annoyed you—}Nếu nó khiến anh tò mò...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You haven't annoyed me!}{\i0}Không có tò mò gì đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But just let me ask you this.}{\i0}Nhưng để tôi xác nhận lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, you used a black rista from House Kiltyrin\Nwithout permission to heal me, right?}{\i0}Jess, cô sử dụng một rista đen từ nhà Kiltyrin\N để chữa cho tôi mà chưa xin phép nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And so you had to use\Nyour own money to replace it.}{\i0}Và giờ phải dùng tiền túi để mua lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd just been reprimanded\Nfor using a yellow rista without permission,}Tôi vừa bị mắng vì sử dụng\N rista vàng mà không xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{so a black rista on top of that\Nwould have been...}Và giờ lại còn cả rista đen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You must've used\Nthat yellow rista on me, too.}{\i0}Cô ấy đã sử dụng cả rista vàng đó vì mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You couldn't have carried me\Nup to the third floor on your own.}{\i0}Cô không thể một mình đưa tôi lên tầng 3 được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So it was all for my sake, huh?}{\i0}Hoá ra tất cả đều vì tôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Everything I did, I did on my own.}Tất cả đều là do tôi tự ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And now I've dragged you into it,\Ntoo, Mister Pig.}Và giờ lại kéo anh vào chuyện này.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Why are you crying?}{\i0}Tại sao cô lại khóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Look at all you did for me!\NAre you feeling bad about that?}{\i0}Nhìn những gì cô làm cho tôi xem! \NVà cô cảm thấy có lỗi vì nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't believe how kind this girl is.}{\i0}Cô gái này quá tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Because she's too kind... Just too kind...}{\i0}Nhưng cũng vì quá tốt bụng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I owe her way more\Nthan I could ever repay as a pig.}{\i0}Nên tôi không thể nào trả lại ơn này được.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't even stroke her head\Nwith my pig feet!}{\i0}Mình còn không thể xoa đầu cô ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thanks, Jess.}{\i0}Cảm ơn Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You didn't do anything wrong.}{\i0}Cô không làm gì sai cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you did make any mistake,}{\i0}Nếu cô có làm gì sai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{it was to get involved in trouble with a human\Nwho'd been turned into a pig! That's it!}{\i0}thì là do bị dính vào một con heo phiền phức, thế thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're no trouble at all. Please...}Anh không có phiền phức. Nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no reason for you to cry, Jess.}{\i0}Cô không cần khóc đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't let me see you like that.\NTry not to for my sake.}{\i0}Đừng cho tôi thấy khuôn mặt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You finally smiled for me, huh?}{\i0}Cuối cùng cũng cười nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No.}{\i0}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You were only trying to make\Nsomething happen because I'd asked you to.}{\i0}Jess chỉ cố gắng làm gì đó vì mình yêu cầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We can't waste any more time!}{\i0}Chúng ta không thể cứ thế này mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I have to pay you back, Jess.}{\i0}Tôi sẽ trả ơn cho cô, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You always buy rista\Nat that shop, right, Jess?}{\i0}Lúc nào cô cũng mua rista ở kia nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The shopkeeper, Mister Kilins,\Nalways treats me kindly.}Chủ cửa hàng, ngài Kilins \Nlúc nào cũng tốt với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, have you ever done\Nsomething called "haggling"?}{\i0}Jess, cô biết từ "mặc cả" không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It would be terrible\Nto cause the shop to suffer any losses.}Sẽ khủng khiếp lắm nếu bắt cửa\N hàng phải chịu tổn thất...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But just having you shop there\Nmust bring in huge profits for them, too.}{\i0}Nhưng bên kia cũng có lợi nếu cô đến mua hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sure they'd be happy\Nto show you a little kindness.}{\i0}Họ sẽ cũng sẽ vui khi thấy khách\N hàng hài lòng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that how it works, I wonder.}Tôi cũng không rõ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes, for sure! Let's just go in!}{\i0}Chắc chắn luôn! Vào thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, hello, Jess!}Xin chào Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey...}Chà...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't usually see you with that one.}Hiếm khi thấy cô đi cùng ai khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hello, Mister Kilins.}Xin chào ngài Kilins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, which rista will it be today?}Thế hôm nay cô mua rista nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um, well...}À vâng...
