Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{200 golts?}200 á?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What are you going to do\Nabout the other 400?}Thế còn 400 kia đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Say, "I really need it,\Nso could you please lower the price?"}{\i0}Nói "Tôi thực sự rất cần, làm ơn hãy giảm giá".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I really need it.}Tôi thực sự cần nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Would you be so kind\Nas to lower the price?}Liệu ngài có thể giảm giá chứ?
