Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Say yes!}{\i0}Nói vâng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, did you see those moves he made?\NLike an injured heckripon!}Thấy mấy bước nhảy đó không?\N Y như quái vật bị thương ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Heckripon? I'm not sure what he means,\Nbut it sounds like he's mocking me!}{\i0}Quái vật? Tuy không hiểu lắm\N nhưng có vẻ mình đang bị sỉ nhục.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Man, I'm thrilled!}Chà, ta vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, Jess,\Nyou can keep your 200 golts!}Được rồi, cô có thể giữ lại 200 đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll trade you a black rista for him!}Ta sẽ đổi 1 rista đen lấy nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, how generous is that!}{\i0}Ồ, quyết định rất dứt khoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm putting on a show\Nduring tonight's festival.}Tối nay ta sẽ dùng nó trình diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And I bet I can make a killing\Nif I use this pig!}Nếu dùng nó ta có thể sẽ thắng giải.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Tonight, huh?}{\i0}Đêm nay à...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If I run off before he makes his killing,\Nhe'll turn his rage onto Jess!}{\i0}Nếu bỏ trốn trước buổi diễn, \Nông ta sẽ trút mọi tức giận lên Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not good! I need a plan!}{\i0}Không ổn! Phải suy nghĩ cách thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um, about the festival...\NPlease let me help you with that, too!}Về lễ hội đó... tôi sẽ giúp nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess! Hold up! If you do that—}{\i0}Này Jess! Dừng lại! Nếu làm thế--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm the one who raised Mister Pig.}Tôi là người nuôi nấng anh Heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd like to see him make his mark.}Nên có tôi sẽ dễ chỉ dẫn hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll serve you free of charge.}Dĩ nhiên là miễn phí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I didn't want to create a situation\Nthat would throw suspicion on Jess.}{\i0}Mình không muốn tạo ra thêm rắc rối cho Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But what about your work\Nfor House Kiltyrin?}Nhưng còn việc của nhà Kiltyrin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If they were to reproach me for this,\NI couldn't hope to stay in business.}Nếu họ khiển trách ta thì khó làm ăn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's all right.}Không sao ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You see, another Yethma is coming\Nto replace me tonight.}Đêm nay sẽ có một Yethma thay thế tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}Phải nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, the time has come already, huh?}Cũng đến thời điểm này rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see. That's why you're selling the pig.}Ra đó là lý do cô bán đi con heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right, gotcha.}Rồi, ta hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll arrange the schedule\Nso you can see the show, so help me out.}Ta sẽ điều chỉnh lịch, hãy giúp ta một tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn ngài rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, come to the town plaza\Nby sundown, then.}Vậy tối nay hãy đến quảng trường thị trấn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir!}Vâng ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Mister Pig.}Xin lỗi anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{For settling things without asking you.}Vì đã tự tiện quyết định.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, no problem!}{\i0}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just make sure you don't help me escape.}{\i0}Chỉ là đừng giúp tôi bỏ trốn là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi không muốn họ nghi ngờ Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Will you be okay?}{\i0}Mọi chuyện sẽ ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sure. Who do you think I am?}{\i0}Cô nghĩ tôi là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm the dirty scrawny four-eyed virgin.}{\i0}Tôi là trai tân 4 mắt gầy gò xấu xí đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It just won't do for you\Nto underestimate me.}{\i0}Đừng xem thường tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Here you go. My parting gift.}Đây. Quà tiễn biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn ngài rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is such great help to me!}Ngài đã giúp đỡ tôi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, I'll be back\Nafter I've run some errands.}Vậy tối tôi sẽ quay lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sure thing. I'm counting on you!}Ừ. Nhờ cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Vậy nhé anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll see you at the festival!}{\i0}Hãy gặp nhau ở lễ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sure! See you!}{\i0}Ừm! Gặp cô sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now then, what am I going to do? Huh?}{\i0}Giờ thì mình làm gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but you'll have to sit still\Nlike a good boy for now...}Xin lỗi nhưng ngươi phải ngoan ngoãn một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig.}Anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}{Even a Pig Will Dance\NIf You Flatter Them Enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, we've got the black rista in hand,\Nbut next up is the escape mission, huh?}{\i0}Đã có rista đen... tiếp theo là nhiệm vụ trốn thoát à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I sure did put on a show for Jess...}{\i0}Mình đã khẳng định chắc nịch với Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but what should I do now?}{\i0}nhưng giờ làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig!}Anh Heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Whoa!}{\i0}Ồ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're in a maid's outfit!}{\i0}Cô mặc đồ hầu gái à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now, if you were to call me "Master"\Nwhile dressed like that...}{\i0}Giờ nếu gọi tôi là chủ nhân nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'd be like, "Oink, oink, oink!"}{\i0}Thì tôi sẽ éc éc éc suốt luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, you mean these.}Cái này á?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought you might be hungry,\Nso I brought these for you.}Tôi nghĩ anh đói nên mang đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please go ahead and eat them...}Hãy ăn nó đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{M-Master.}C-Chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oink!}{\i0}Éc!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thank you!}{\i0}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I shall partake!}{\i0}Ăn ngay khi còn ấm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Mmm, these sure are tasty!}{\i0}Ngon quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I owe you big time!}{\i0}Nợ cô lần này!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Jess, let's decide on a place to meet\Nafter I've escaped.}{\i0}Jess, hãy quyết định\N nơi gặp nhau sau khi tôi thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A place to meet?}{\i0}Nơi gặp nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's see.}{\i0}Xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Where should it be?}{\i0}Ở đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you going back to House Kiltyrin\Nafter the festival?}{\i0}Cô không định quay lại nhà Kiltyrin à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes.}{\i0}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Since I have to prepare for my trip.}{\i0}Tôi đã chuẩn bị cho chuyến đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then, how about that spot under the big tree\Nyou took me to this morning?}{\i0}Vậy dưới cái cây to\N cô dẫn tôi đến lúc sáng thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll figure something out by daybreak.}{\i0}Bình minh lên tôi sẽ tìm ra cách.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, come to that spot\Nwhen the sun starts rising.}{\i0}Hãy đến đó trước khi mặt trời mọc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Understood.}{\i0}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't worry, Jess.}{\i0}Đừng lo Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Who do you think I am?}{\i0}Cô nghĩ tôi là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're Mister Dirty Scrawny\NFour-eyed Virgin, right?}{\i0}Là anh chàng 4 mắt gầy gò xấu xí còn trinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not that that's my name.}{\i0}Cái đó không phải tên tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Right.}{\i0}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't you underestimate me!}{\i0}Đừng xem thường tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll bust out, no matter what!}{\i0}Nhất định sẽ thoát được.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So don't worry about a thing!}{\i0}Đừng lo gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Understood.}{\i0}Tôi hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then I'll trust you!}{\i0}Tôi sẽ tin anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
